    <div class="md:w-3/4">
      <h2
        class="font-heading font-bold text-[28px] text-brand-primary uppercase mb-4"
      >
        The Foundation: Medical Diagnosis
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-brand-text text-[17px] leading-[37px] mb-4">
        Remember that an effective treatment is only possible with a diagnosis
        that gets to the absolute bottom of the problem. <a
          href="/en/medical-diagnosis/"
          class="text-brand-secondary underline hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors"
          >General Medical Diagnosis using bio-frequencies</a
        > is the tool that allows us to create a precise map of your health condition,
        identify the original root causes, and design a truly customized and highly
        effective treatment plan.
      </p>
      <blockquote
        class="italic text-gray-600 border-l-4 border-brand-accent pl-4 font-body leading-[37px]"
      >
        <strong>Important Note:</strong> Our list of treatments is only a general
        guide. If your specific condition does not appear here, please do not hesitate
        to contact me. The holistic approach and the sophisticated tools I use allow
        us to address a vast array of health imbalances.
      </blockquote>
